      "para_id": "Q001629.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Inana , lady of the E-ana , his lady , Ur-Namma , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , dug the Iturungal canal , her beloved canal ."
    }
